Usage: writeAnnotatedTransition [-help] [-direct] -file <string> [-max] [-min]
                                [-noPort] [-view <string>] [-writeOutput]

-help                    # Prints out the command usage
-direct                  # Refers the ports directly. (bool, optional)
-file <string>           # Output file name. (string, required)
-max                     # Specify whether to write out max. transition
                         # (bool, optional)
-min                     # Specify whether to write out min. transition
                         # (bool, optional)
-noPort                  # Skip write the transition values for the primary
                         # ports. (bool, optional)
-view <string>           # View name for the output file. (string, optional)
-writeOutput             # Also write the slews for output pins and output slew
                         # for bidir pins. (bool, optional)